{"tid":1302053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"社會信用機制發威 逾千萬人次被限購機票","createTime":"2019-07-09T22:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T23:37:08.000Z","uid":219729,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"608f247b62e7d791fa4d2b20a631fbe54ab7618b","tid":1302053,"uid":219729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:52:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/shehui/hc-05182018110948.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fshehui%2Fhc-05182018110948.html%2FampRFA&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=07f108fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/shehui/hc-05182018110948.html/ampRFA</a><br />\n<br />\n引起媒體廣泛關注的中國社會信用體系的執行力度現已初見端倪。據報道，目前已有逾千萬人次被限購機票或高鐵動車票。龐大數字的背後究竟反映了政府怎樣的社會管理理念呢？<br />\n<br />\n據《南方都市報》近期報道，截至4月底，因信用記錄不佳，中國全國累計限制購買飛機票超過了1100萬人次，而限制購買高鐵動車票達到了425萬人次。另外，法院公佈的失信被執行人中，近250萬人因懲戒選擇主動履行義務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解冇乜人講呢個社會信用機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n惡過送中好多"},{"pid":"546c4bcf719b82b0b28b05bbf0305e61d74ebfb4","tid":1302053,"uid":219729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:52:33.000Z","msg":"社會信用評分系統懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300184</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a020b45e01d24f8c388b04f7504fc4273102918","tid":1302053,"uid":219729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:53:00.000Z","msg":"社會信用體系？其實港共已經開始左！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b40ef330662a1e97baff239c496de9a28c36bdc5","tid":1302053,"uid":219729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T22:53:27.000Z","msg":"急! 突發，3年內將引入「社會信用評分系統」。文宣組幫幫手<br />\n